React.ReactElement<any,string|React.JSXE.description:
Represents a JSX element.

Where {@link ReactNode} represents everything that can be rendered, `ReactElement`
only represents JSX.

props.description: The type of the props object

type.description: The type of the component or tag

React.ReactNode.description:
Represents all of the things React can render.

Where {@link ReactElement} only represents JSX, `ReactNode` represents everything that can be rendered.

props.description: The type of the props object

type.description: The type of the component or tag

base.description: Set base classes for the root element.

classes.description: Provide arbitrary classes to the root element.

describedBy.description: Identifies the element that describes the switch.

height.description: Set height classes for the root element.

hover.description: Set hover classes for the root element.

iconActiveBase.description: Set base classes for the active icon child.

iconInactiveBase.description: Set base classes for the inactive icon child.

id.description: Set a unique ID for the switch input.

labelledBy.description: Identifies the element that labels the switch.

name.description: Set a unique name for the switch input.

onChange.description: Triggers when the switch is toggled.

padding.description: Set padding classes for the root element.

rounded.description: Set rounded classes for the root element.

stateActive.description: Set active state classes for the root element.

stateDisabled.description: Set disabled state classes for the root element.

stateInactive.description: Set inactive state classes for the root element.

thumbActive.description: Set active classes for the thumb element.

thumbBase.description: Set base classes for the thumb element.

thumbClasses.description: Provide arbitrary classes to the thumb element.

thumbDuration.description: Set animation duration classes for the thumb element.

thumbEase.description: Set animation easing classes for the thumb element.

thumbInactive.description: Set inactive classes for the thumb element.

thumbRounded.description: Set rounded classes for the thumb element.

thumbTransition.description: Set animation transition classes for the thumb element.

thumbTranslateX.description: Set animation X-axis translate classes for the thumb element.

width.description: Set width classes for the root element.
